						<summary>

						<p>Another broken slab lying on the river bank to the north-east of the village.</p>						

						<p>Tirukālattidēva Chōḍa Mahārāja I.</p>						

						<p>This dated in the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Vibhava, Chitra śu. 8, Thursday.</hi> In characters of 8th century A.D.</p>						

						<p>Records the gift of land for the worship and offerings to the god Rāmīśvara by certain individual Bhīmi-Nāhiḍu and a gift to another individual Kaṇṭha Jiya.</p>						

						</summary>
